;Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:19.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.46,0:09:23.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚了一步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.09,0:09:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫他等等我們就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.01,0:09:28.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  真的被釋放了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.47,0:09:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,證據不足嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過他也因為ZERO的事  被好好調查了一番
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.07,0:09:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:41.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不擅長和貓交流嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.78,0:09:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.55,0:09:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過總是我單戀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.66,0:09:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會單戀的是很溫柔的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.27,0:09:55.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.67,0:09:57.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤菲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.15,0:10:00.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才為什麼撒那樣的謊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在意我的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?  啊  是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.63,0:10:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就再陪陪我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.40,0:10:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:20.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和在布里塔尼亞的時候沒什麼不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤菲是從本國來的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.38,0:10:24.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是學生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到上周為止還是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:27.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上周為止還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼現在呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:29.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生是指高中生?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要觀光的話什麼時候都可以吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:38.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.39,0:10:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  因為今天是假期的最後一天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.77,0:10:44.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以很想來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看AREA-11
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.26,0:10:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡到底是怎麼樣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.22,0:10:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  不用找我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.79,0:10:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我很高興是你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:53.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.01,0:10:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.45,0:10:59.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否請你再帶我去一個地方呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.33,0:11:02.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬請吩咐  公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:04.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 去新宿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.59,0:11:08.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我看一看新宿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.26,0:11:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樞木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:19.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在方便嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:23.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:25.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於之前電話的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.25,0:11:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.68,0:11:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  就是在浴室的那次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.51,0:11:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能查一下來電記錄?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.66,0:11:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和對方聯繫一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.26,0:11:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是學校的電話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:41.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.98,0:11:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊  果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:45.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼? 怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:48.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.99,0:11:52.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.84,0:11:58.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.87,0:12:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是什麼意思呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然會以這種形式回本國
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當初不和那個女人扯上關係就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.13,0:12:13.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要到處亂逛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.10,0:12:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂吧  反正是在學校內而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.41,0:12:18.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說得那麼嚴厲嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.89,0:12:19.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.97,0:12:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡可是個外人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:24.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在哪裡都是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.36,0:12:29.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 今天也在做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.09,0:12:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.08,0:12:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對她使用了Geass  讓她每天都來這牆上做標記
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:39.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Geass?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.45,0:12:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是指這個力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:42.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在締結契約的時候 我聽到是這麼叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.55,0:12:46.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做關於持續時間的實驗嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器的特性是應該要充分理解的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:51.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你太任性的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.27,0:12:52.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我會有效果嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.45,0:12:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我是共犯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:13:01.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會做對我們不利的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.28,0:13:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新宿貧民區  已經完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.71,0:13:12.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易人們開始回到這個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:23.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 對付ELEVEN還不需要用到RG呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.27,0:13:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  這邊有對人炮彈的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.85,0:13:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.96,0:13:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著到我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.17,0:13:31.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:34.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎  關於ZERO的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是丘威爾卿那裡傳來的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.14,0:13:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將新宿貧民區第四區域設置為緊急狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[大公(Grand duke): 是西歐、尤其是日耳曼語族國家的爵位之一\N低於國王(King等)、高於公爵(Duke, Herzog，Furst等)]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  大公
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:46.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丘威爾卿  之後就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本來這是想和傑雷米亞卿聯繫的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.48,0:13:53.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過看樣子現在不是說這個的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:13:55.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我滾出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亞的豬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:13:59.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.50,0:14:00.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.55,0:14:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是ELEVEN嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是日本人!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.60,0:14:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准叫ELEVEN!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.66,0:14:05.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們輸給我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.00,0:14:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰敗國的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個布里塔尼亞的混蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:10.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要用暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.60,0:14:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別妨礙我們!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.31,0:14:16.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.34,0:14:18.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你… 是樞木朱雀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.47,0:14:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了克洛維斯的樞木?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  是ZERO殺的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.01,0:14:25.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙只是個奴隸而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:28.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼名譽布里塔尼亞人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.54,0:14:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己還一副高興的樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.06,0:14:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尊嚴  同伴  甚至連靈魂都出賣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.44,0:14:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣還算是日本人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.08,0:14:35.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對!  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.41,0:14:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼不對的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這條布里塔尼亞的走狗!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.83,0:14:44.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是接受過訓練的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.48,0:14:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再對同伴…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.36,0:14:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  已經夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:14:57.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.99,0:15:03.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.71,0:15:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.08,0:15:07.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.65,0:15:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我引以為傲的G-MX4啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太慢了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.86,0:15:13.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  虧你還是個名譽布里塔尼亞人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:15.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼讓他們跑了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.98,0:15:16.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了他們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:19.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你也殺了很多ELEVEN了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.63,0:15:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為是誰在養你啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.87,0:15:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不允許你再侮辱這個人!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.67,0:15:32.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要使用Geass 必須直視對方的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.79,0:15:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼鏡這種程度的穿透沒什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.44,0:15:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有效距離大約是270米左右
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.21,0:15:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  被施予Geass的前後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:42.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及期間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:44.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會產生記憶缺損
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可以認為是Geass介入大腦所造成的損傷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.89,0:15:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果它是光信息的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反射也是可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那麼短的時間內居然能調查到這個程度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.63,0:16:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手可是控制了世界三分之一以上的帝國啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:02.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼謹慎也不為過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是ELEVEN的話還能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:05.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你是布里塔尼亞人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:07.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅憑借Geass去戰鬥的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:10.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手未免也太強大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.95,0:16:12.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要強大就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.31,0:16:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱小是不行的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.59,0:16:18.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.86,0:16:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在年僅10歲的我們看來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.48,0:16:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界看起來非常的悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飢餓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:27.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疾病
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:29.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貪污  腐敗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:30.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歧視
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.23,0:16:32.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭以及恐怖活動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.23,0:16:35.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複不斷的憎恨的連鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢無謂的循環
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須有人來斬斷這個連鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:44.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是理想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:48.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  我沒有想過能讓這一切全部消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:50.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒有傲慢到那個程度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:51.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:54.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠不失去最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.62,0:16:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少  一個沒有戰爭的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.08,0:16:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種理想的世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:17:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼做…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.02,0:17:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.56,0:17:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要某個人贏了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭就能結束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,0:17:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某個人?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.47,0:17:11.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也還不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.31,0:17:14.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果放棄追求的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.14,0:17:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親就白白犧牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:18.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樞木首相嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那場戰爭中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.84,0:17:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親不得不死…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.83,0:17:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑雷米亞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:30.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放任殺害克洛維斯殿下的兇手逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.46,0:17:31.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這責任就用你的命來償還吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.18,0:17:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙的丘威爾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.81,0:17:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說發現了ZERO是謊言嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在柯內莉婭殿下到任前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.63,0:17:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要先清除內部的恥辱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:42.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑雷米亞  這是肅清
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.12,0:17:47.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞希爾小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.14,0:17:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡很危險  快上來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.99,0:17:51.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純血派的內訌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.37,0:17:54.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  還有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.35,0:17:55.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被無罪釋放真是遺憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.08,0:17:57.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要讓你陪我們研究了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:17:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:18:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不正是取得Lancelot戰鬥數據的好機會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:05.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.92,0:18:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  尤菲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就在這裡分別吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不得不去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.26,0:18:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是Lancelot的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.66,0:18:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該可以阻止他們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.55,0:18:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.88,0:18:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然四個一起上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:20.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙小人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:23.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  傑雷米亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.38,0:18:24.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對外會把你當成戰死來處理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.03,0:18:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你家族的名譽受損的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.22,0:18:28.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.65,0:18:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要把我給…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丘威爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.58,0:18:33.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴  ORANGE
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:35.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是為了什麼而存在的?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.89,0:18:37.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了皇室!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All Hail Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.23,0:18:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.36,0:18:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同為布里塔尼亞軍的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是  名譽布里塔尼亞人的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.80,0:18:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚮導兵器  Lancelot
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.52,0:18:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別派遣有何貴幹?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.16,0:18:59.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是誰  只要介入一律殺無赦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.72,0:19:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.23,0:19:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法坐視無意義的戰鬥而不加理會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.32,0:19:09.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[MVS：Maser Vibration Sword的縮寫，鐳射振動劍\N利用微波鐳射振動製作的斬擊用武器]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.32,0:19:09.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MVS?  已經投入實戰了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.22,0:19:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  事到如今 沒有退路了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:15.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都是同伴 為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.15,0:19:22.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我也救?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.84,0:19:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樞木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.03,0:19:32.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  即使只是殺死ORANGE也好…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.04,0:19:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑雷米亞卿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:38.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[維蕾塔·紐 Villetta Nu]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:37.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維蕾塔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.04,0:19:38.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.94,0:19:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還打算繼續嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.48,0:19:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家退後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.85,0:19:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丘威爾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:50.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你終於能理解了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:53.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要使用CHAOS爆雷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.29,0:19:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:19:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:23.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個名譽布里塔尼亞人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.88,0:20:25.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然挺身涉險…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.64,0:20:27.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙方都請收起手中的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:32.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我之名下令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.97,0:20:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難… 難道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.60,0:20:36.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是布里塔尼亞第三皇女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:39.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[Euphemia Li Britannia]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤菲米婭·Li·布里塔尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤菲?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:43.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這裡由我來指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都退下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:48.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是… 皇女殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.84,0:20:50.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是知道的嗎?  羅伊德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.76,0:20:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因為是學生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.03,0:20:55.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不常拋頭露面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.57,0:20:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實… 實在是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.11,0:21:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是罪該萬死!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇女殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.46,0:21:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然事先不知
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.89,0:21:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是請恕我先前失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.48,0:21:10.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.80,0:21:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同你失去了父親一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.91,0:21:15.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也失去了兄長克洛維斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今以後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.24,0:21:20.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了創造不再失去重要之人的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.17,0:21:22.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否助我一臂之力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.31,0:21:27.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是!  不勝榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.86,0:21:32.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說了  尤菲米婭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:33.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別太亂來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.45,0:21:36.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉 皇姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.43,0:21:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.62,0:21:39.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種場合請叫我總督
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.32,0:21:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤菲米婭副總督
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.03,0:21:43.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為我們是親姐妹 所以更需要劃清界限
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.01,0:21:45.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.64,0:21:49.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  那邊的情況怎樣了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:55.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  在政廳已經準備好了盛大的宴會歡迎皇女殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.97,0:22:01.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得鬆懈  變得糊塗  變得墮落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.70,0:22:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO的事怎樣了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.15,0:22:05.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去逮捕帝國臣民的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.41,0:22:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.94,0:22:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是從今天開始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.77,0:22:13.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉入這所阿斯福德學園學習的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.02,0:22:15.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樞木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.51,0:22:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.72,0:23:50.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.22,0:23:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.99,0:23:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對莎莉和利瓦爾他們
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.64,0:23:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至連朱雀和娜娜莉也…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.66,0:23:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是已經沒有退路了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.07,0:23:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經無法回頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.96,0:24:01.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然C.C.說是共犯的話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.23,0:24:03.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就做共犯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.92,0:24:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經  不想對自己撒謊了
